[Student "S"]
{EAST bids 3\S to show a strong hand with a singleton \S. 

After WEST shows her first-round \C control EAST decides he will bid slam if WEST has three Aces.

When Blackwood reveals just two Aces in WEST, EAST stops at 5\H.}

